# Installer build artifacts (publish staging + generated MSI/EXE bundle/PDB/wixpdb).
# The 60 MB+ self-contained installers are release deliverables, not source, so
# they stay out of history — both where the build writes them (installer\) and
# where build-msi.bat copies them (repo root).
installer/publish/
installer/*.msi
installer/*.exe
installer/*.wixpdb
/LithicBackup-*-x64.msi
/LithicBackup-*-x64.exe
